%F A025981 a(n) = 26*a(n-1) - 227*a(n-2) + 754*a(n-3) - 792*a(n-4), a(0)=1, a(1)=26, a(2)=449, a(3)=6526. - _Harvey P. Dale_, Aug 11 2012
%F A025981 a(n) = -4*2^n/63 + 32*4^n/35 - 729*9^n/70 + 1331*11^n/126. - _R. J. Mathar_, Jun 20 2013
%F A025981 a(n) = (4^(n+1)-2^(n+1))/2+20*a(n-1)-99*a(n-2). - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Jul 02 2026
